1. *Životom* se bori za svoj cilj. (She is fighting for her goal with her life.)
2. On se *životom* bori protiv nepravde. (He is fighting against injustice with his life.) 
3. Moraće da se *životima* bore za svoja prava. (They will have to fight for their rights with their lives.) 
4. *Životom* se bore za bolji svet. (They are fighting for a better world with their lives.) 
5. Oni se *životom* bore za slobodu. (They are fighting for freedom with their lives.)